{"tid":1029063,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪玩轉嘉年華　贏巨型熊公仔","createTime":"2019-02-20T03:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T07:21:20.000Z","uid":9573,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"559a7dfd845593bc6c00869a0ecbba7cb623a9f7","tid":1029063,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190219/photo/bkn-20190219173052206-0219_00862_001_05b.jpg?20190219184518\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190219%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190219173052206-0219_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20190219184518&h=0d15acbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人岑杏賢（Jennifer）同朱千雪向來都係好姊姊，不時結伴周圍去。近日佢兩個就去咗嘉年華玩，贏到隻巨型熊公仔，佢哋話初頭估唔到會掟中，點知去到最後一個圈真係畀佢哋中咗，開心到尖叫咗好耐！Jennifer話：「If you all wonder, bear and I are getting on quite well, he only takes up half of my sofa ... but no complaining Got lucky in the Year of Convo of the day（雖然熊仔佔咗我大半張梳化，不過我唔會投訴，因為係一個好意頭。）」網民話咁大隻公仔都畀佢哋贏到，讚佢哋好叻叻呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/361922/org/1851d26c337a72156c2780a920cb730a.jpg/8l-sFq33tOO_w2wDDUP0x3oC_jbQN_OgduBBlXbgQZU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F361922%2Forg%2F1851d26c337a72156c2780a920cb730a.jpg%2F8l-sFq33tOO_w2wDDUP0x3oC_jbQN_OgduBBlXbgQZU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8b2d94fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190219/photo/bkn-20190219173052206-0219_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190219184518\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190219%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190219173052206-0219_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190219184518&h=3c0d9bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190219/photo/bkn-20190219173052206-0219_00862_001_03b.jpg?20190219184518\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on